Night in the Woods Wierd Autumn Edition-RELOADED

  College dropout Mae Borowski returns home to the crumbling former mining
  town of Possum Springs seeking to resume her aimless former life and
  reconnect with the friends she left behind. But things aren't the same.
  Home seems different now and her friends have grown and changed. Leaves are
  falling and the wind is growing colder. Strange things are happening as the
